VIS - The ultimate vim command launcher !

Vim Instant Sight is a commande that will allways open vim in a session related to the current branch of the git repository you are in.


// INSTALL

Import this script in your .bashrc


// REQUIREMENTS

You'll need:
- vim SessionMan : http://www.vim.org/scripts/script.php?script_id=2010
- git (of course)
- vim (of course)


// USAGE

- type 'vis' and that's all, it will take care of everything
- you can also type 'vis somesession' to force open/create a specific session

